Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.31,0:00:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Since the audition for the commercial was canceled...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she had a long break before returning to work.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.86,0:00:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.56,0:00:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there was a rumor about {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  going around at the television station...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.40,0:00:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}On top of that...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...at some point, someone tore apart her costume...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.11,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and we were in a huge bind! {Oh Nippon and your dai pinchii}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But even in such a bind...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Mitsuki came up with an idea to overcome it...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and the television program finished without a hitch.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...this girl's become so strong!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.09,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My first solo live concert?!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.14,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You think it might be a little too early, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's been a huge response from the fans!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That means that...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they'll all want to go to the live concert!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are they for real?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.82,0:00:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's like a dream come true...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Getting to hear you say such adorable things...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There won't be much time for that now...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Things are going to be hectic from here on out.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You'll lose all of your summer vacation...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.32,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...so be ready!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, regarding that...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For your first live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is there anything special you'd like to try out?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.08,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you asking... me?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.82,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just how does {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  feel about this right now...?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My feelings right now?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't there something?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}An image... or a keyword...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.05,0:01:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anything's okay, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...just tell us.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe that's asking for too much, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.83,0:01:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.48,0:01:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll do it!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:32.53,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\pos(320,340)\bord2.5}Exciting Solo Live Concert
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:37.04,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.99,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.63,0:01:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll be going over the essential parts of a live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and explaining the–
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.92,0:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give it up.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I give up on this!
