Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.64,0:01:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...to have a good live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...things like your image...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and theme are important!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.51,0:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... in that case...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...when it comes to time to prepare...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...things will get ugly if you have to worry about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Meroko's going to help you this time.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said, that's just...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm already...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...far too brilliant...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.40,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's like I'm the number one bride for any Shinigami.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's way out there...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.57,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone else thinks so...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.08,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.08,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Listen to people when they're talking!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki already knows all of that.
