Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.58,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She does?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.99,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... what are you planning on doing...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...for {\i1}Full Moon{\i0} 's first live concert?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's Moon and Stars.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Moon and Stars?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.80,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The theme of {\i1}Full Moon{\i0} 's first live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Moon and Stars, has been decided.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Decided?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.67,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.85,0:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You never told me that it was already decided!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.07,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've been trying to tell you the whole time, but you haven't been listening!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm heartbroken...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for being so concerned about everything, Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Actually, you see...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is being broadcast to everyone around the world through the Internet. {TEH INTARWEBZ}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.48,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So... surely...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.68,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Moon and Stars...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.92,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To the moon and the stars...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.75,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll send my feelings for Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.88,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and sing with all my heart!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be sure to watch, Eichi-kun!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I can't... {\alpha&Hff&}I... I-I can't... I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I can't... I... {\alpha&Hff&}I-I can't... I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I can't... I... I-I can't... {\alpha&Hff&}I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I can't... I... I-I can't... I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For the location of {\i1}Full Moon{\i0} 's first live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we've decided on Bayside Hall.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We'll open at five...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'll start at six, so make sure everyone knows.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As for the visual effects and stage lighting...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they were finished yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What about the musicians?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We already got the best of the best!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.83,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The backup chorus is perfect as well!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have all the dancers been gathered?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We've got experienced foreign dancers ready to go!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't this perfect?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Damn good job...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.25,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... I thought of it earlier, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.44,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What if...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.12,0:04:38.93,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.42,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...to put together my first live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.24,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they're all working so hard...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Boss!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're done printing!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh ho...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(30,450)}{\an1}Nice!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(610,450)}{\an3}They're great!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow! It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah, it looks good.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.61,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With this, Moon and Stars... will be on its way!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is my first live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Moon and Stars!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So then...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...everything's still in the process of being set up, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sure it'll be a great live concert!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone, please come and listen, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good luck!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll come up with the perfect advertisement.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.77,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To tell the truth...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...my own kids are huge fans, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be there with my kids to listen.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good luck.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.15,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here you go.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Akiba-san, I definitely want you to come listen!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is the greatest!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.36,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Such a great seat at your first live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Put these posters everywhere \Naround the store, 'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-oneechan!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm cheering for you, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you have to have a cool live concert!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Got it!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can count on me.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto's going to cheer along with me!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.91,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Promise!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'kay. It's a promise!
