Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh, good luck on your live concert!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.41,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're rooting for you!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.33,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Komaki-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.82,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Heh...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.47,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}First live concert, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everybody!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come hear me at my first live concert, 'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is where the live concert will be held.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's huge!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You'll sing on much bigger stages.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you're scared by just this, it'll be problematic.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can I try standing on it?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is your stage.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.82,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(0,2100)}I'm gonna give it my all!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.06,0:08:30.03,Transparent Echo,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\alpha99}{\an7\fad(210,420)\pos(50,5)}I'm gonna give it my all!
