Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm home...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.28,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aren't you late?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.58,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh my, already?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At least change your clothes first.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You have to take proper care of your skin.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wake up!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}First solo live concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Moon and Stars...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please come listen...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My, my, my... she's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man, guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do your best!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good night.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.06,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come in!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you done?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.14,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's good, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it seems to lack that {\i1}oomph.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It feels like something's missing.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shall we throw on some accessories, then? {shani: accessories? like really? :D}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In addition...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...let's try some makeup and add a little color.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.08,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? {\alpha&Hff&}Eh? {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.74,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? Eh? {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How's this?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In that case, I'll go even farther!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... {\alpha&Hff&}ah... ah-choo!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... ah... {\alpha&Hff&}ah-choo!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.11,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... ah... ah-choo!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll get that off right away!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did I forget to bring it?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.68,0:10:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(297.143,450)}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(425,450)}Huh? {separate}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm done!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's Moon and Stars!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep. It's cute.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's taken care of.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do her costume fitting now.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so wonderful!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just tried to add something extra.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you, Machi-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So now, then..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...all that's left is the accessories...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... the theme is...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.33,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Moon and Stars! {these splits are kinda annoying at times}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.31,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In that case, let's make this a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see... next comes... this one.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.19,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or is this one better...?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But I wanna go to sleep already!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're the one who wanted to help.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Far too brilliant...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The best choice for a bride, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.28,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}It's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:26.89,0:12:27.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Mitsuki... just like the moon and the stars that shine in the sky...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}...there will surely come a time where you shine as well.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.64,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've sent my wish to the moon and the stars...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.64,0:12:44.23,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why I chose Moon and Stars...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.36,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.92,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to shine!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.36,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In order for Eichi-kun to find me...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In order to reach everyone who's cheering for me...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's done!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's finished?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.78,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll try this color next.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is taking a lot longer than I expected.
