Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This will work.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone will fall in love with \Nthat accessory instantly!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.11,0:13:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-There's a problem!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.77,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.19,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the site's been canceled!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.74,0:13:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The live concert's tomorrow!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.02,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone called saying that they were a member of the Village Pro staff...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and told them that tomorrow's live concert for {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  has been put on hold.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's complete nonsense!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone go tell them about this... fix it before it's too late!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...another event was scheduled immediately after...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.36,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All the posters and tickets are already out!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.90,0:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, divide everyone and get on the phones!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't matter where!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just find an open place!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.98,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!   Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes... tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's the day after today!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How can we find a place that fast?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If we can't find a place...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we'll have to postpone the live concert.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That can't be...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.96,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what you deserve.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you help us out somehow?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I beg you!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, can you come back later?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're already booked.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm begging you!
