Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can sing anywhere!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Set up the lights over there.
