Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.49,0:17:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If we don't hurry, we won't make it before the live concert starts!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.21,0:17:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The location for {\i1}Full Moon{\i0} 's concert has changed!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This way!
