Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry to keep everyone waiting!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}On this, the last evening of the summer...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...let's all have one last blast!
