Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:16.21,Myself IN22 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:22.68,Myself IN22 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,1512)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:41.82,Myself IN22 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I lost way too much back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.20,Myself IN22 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I couldn't sing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:50.66,Myself IN22 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}That place you had to leave for a while...
