Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:04.64,Myself IN22 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:09.77,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)\pos(330,465)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:15.31,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:22.65,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:28.91,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:34.92,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:41.01,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:48.97,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,840)}Until we became so far apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:21:02.32,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,0)}Why is it that I've fallen in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:11.41,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,1470)}I can't find an answer easily...
